{"tid":2003851,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"如果屋企仲有口罩 盡量唔好攞政府布口罩","createTime":"2020-05-06T05:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T06:06:07.000Z","uid":6280,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a8285eb897368304f7a266acb7222db8f99b47","tid":2003851,"uid":6280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:32:37.000Z","msg":"唔講登記資料啲私隱問題<br />\n<br />\n布口罩要自己洗，你肯定屋企啲老人家識得handle<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整濕個口罩嗰時要小心污糟水周圍彈，又要用啱濃度嘅消毒劑<br />\n<br />\n個口罩咁厚，仲要確保佢乾透先戴得<br />\n未乾反而更加容易積菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋話要印乾，唔可以擰乾，啲廢老唔知道又照擰<br />\n一陣個罩耗損咗仲易中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以好似醫療用品咁，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>可以用即棄嘅嘢就即棄，避免重用</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b07d25e57db5755f788fa1b8d1c11fdc0fea185d","tid":2003851,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞嚟擺既姐"},{"pid":"05f77a764ad14e7c3e3495d9536af9678989cc45","tid":2003851,"uid":349976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07d25e57db5755f788fa1b8d1c11fdc0fea185d","tid":2003851,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞嚟擺既姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:38:40.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"be1d5c52220f60e863a49fa521d1c7812949e036","tid":2003851,"uid":267801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"政府派遊行時用，全部人用同一款仲難認。"},{"pid":"9ae54188eee19fda4f45457fc69c06710784cad9","tid":2003851,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be1d5c52220f60e863a49fa521d1c7812949e036","tid":2003851,"uid":267801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"政府派遊行時用，全部人用同一款仲難認。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴左可能明明冇事都變有事<br />\n真係想咁做要擺起碼14日先戴"},{"pid":"5107a944bae54f031321536153f66a57387659c4","tid":2003851,"uid":6280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07d25e57db5755f788fa1b8d1c11fdc0fea185d","tid":2003851,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞嚟擺既姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"如果屋企有老人家，你攞咗佢哋一定會用布口罩，唔用即棄口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢哋一定會想慳得就慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee90a201456b9fe0fb88d268c615d982c8eea8f","tid":2003851,"uid":6280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"身邊好多朋友父母都好慳口罩用<br />\n所以我先得出咁嘅結論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f32b8af1e29f727a4d86ad1323cc9e5badc9dd","tid":2003851,"uid":6280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"或者攞完收起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n減低重用口罩嘅風險<br />\n<br />\n反正政府洗嘅係我哋嘅錢，點都攞返個好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a84a52978eff632133ef4565ee030394008ea8b","tid":2003851,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5107a944bae54f031321536153f66a57387659c4","tid":2003851,"uid":6280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07d25e57db5755f788fa1b8d1c11fdc0fea185d","tid":2003851,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞嚟擺既姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"